SUMMARY:Queer Prom
DESCRIPTION:The LGBTQ+ Cultural Center cordially invites you to join us f
 or a night of magical elegance at Queer Prom 2026: Enchanted Forest!  If 
 you're a lover of whimsy\, wonder\, and woodland fantasy aesthetics\, thi
 s event promises an evening filled with music\, enchantment\, and the cha
 nce to mingle with other radiant\, ethereal souls in a space where everyo
 ne can be mystical royalty.  Step into a realm of twinkling lights\, lush
  greenery\, and otherworldly charm as you dance the night away and live o
 ut your enchanted fairytale dreams. Everyone is invited to find their mom
 ent of magic in a night where community\, imagination\, and queer joy rei
 gn supreme.  Dress to impress in your most spellbinding attire and prepar
 e to be swept into the forest's embrace!All Indiana University events\, g
 roups\, activities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical observan
 ces welcome all IU students and other members of the Indiana University c
 ommunity.
