SUMMARY:Queer Art Showcase
DESCRIPTION:The LGBTQ+ Cultural Center invites you to join us for our Que
 er Art Showcase 2026\, an evening dedicated to celebrating the creativity
 \, expression\, and voices of our community.  This showcase will feature 
 work from queer artists across a variety of mediums. Whether you are an a
 rtist yourself or simply appreciate the power of queer storytelling\, thi
 s event offers a space to explore work that reflects our histories\, iden
 tities\, and imaginations.  Guests are welcome to browse the gallery and 
 engage in conversation about the themes and experiences represented in th
 eir work. The evening is designed to highlight talent and creators in the
  IU community whose perspectives offer an insight into the queer experien
 ce.  &#160\;All Indiana University events\, groups\, activities\, and edu
 cational\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome all IU students 
 and other members of the Indiana University community.
