 wcase will feature work from queer artists across a variety of mediums. W
 hether you are an artist yourself or simply appreciate the power of queer
  storytelling\, this event offers a space to explore work that reflects o
 ur histories\, identities\, and imaginations.</p><p data-end="876" data-s
 tart="586">  Guests are welcome to browse the gallery and engage in conve
 rsation about the themes and experiences represented in their work. The e
 vening is designed to highlight talent and creators in the IU community w
 hose perspectives offer an insight into the queer experience.</p><p data-
